  <description>
    <p>Aliza MS is a standalone medical DICOM viewer</p>
    <ul>
      <li>2D and 3D views with many tools</li>
      <li>3D view also for non-uniform images</li>
      <li>Volume Rendering</li>
      <li>Multi-planar reconstruction (MPR)</li>
      <li>Fast directory scanner, DICOMDIR</li>
      <li>Consistently de-identify DICOM, maintain integrity</li>
      <li>RTSTRUCT contours</li>
      <li>DICOM Study multi-view with intersection lines and side-by-side view</li>
      <li>Proper measurement in Ultrasound Calibrated Regions</li>
      <li>2D+t and 3D+t animations</li>
      <li>DICOM metadata viewer, DICOM 2024b dictionary</li>
      <li>Encapsulated transfer syntaxes incl. HTJ2K</li>
      <li>Most IODs are supported incl. Structured Reports, Key Objects Selection, Grayscale Softcopy Presentation State</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
